      <th>Notes</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>Low-Income Renter<br />(~$30K income)</td>
      <td>$1,600</td>
      <td>$0</td>
      <td><strong>–$1,600</strong></td>
      <td>Benefit: no land ownership, avoids income & sales taxes</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Middle-Income Homeowner<br />(~$120K income, $800K property)</td>
      <td>$11,500</td>
      <td>$31,200</td>
      <td><strong>+$19,700</strong></td>
      <td>Potentially worse off if land value is high</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>High-Income Owner<br />(~$1.2M income, $6M land)</td>
      <td>$118,500</td>
