      <td><strong>Commercial Landowner<br />($30M property, $10.5M land)</strong></td>
      <td>$390,000</td>
      <td>$1,365,000</td>
      <td><strong>+$975,000</strong></td>
      <td>Incentive to develop or intensify land use</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

